What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Cloud Kitchen Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Cloud Kitchen Market

The cloud kitchen market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 10.0% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028 and is expected to reach the value of USD 72,000.0 million by 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on cloud kitchen market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth. Rapid urbanization is escalating the growth of cloud kitchen market.

Cloud kitchens, also called dark or shared kitchens, refer to the delivery-only kitchens that are generally owned by a brand or third party working with various brands. Cloud kitchens offer the capability of operating virtual restaurants or brick-and-mortar restaurant to the brands.

The rise of on-demand food delivery across the globe acts as one of the major factors driving the growth of cloud kitchen market. The increase in the adoption of cloud kitchens or virtual or ghost kitchens, as they are considered more affordable than conventional kitchens in dine-in restaurants, and no requirement of dine-in facilities or account for costs related to location and property accelerate the market growth. The rise in demand for cloud kitchens owning to the flexibility of operating ghost kitchens from any location, ranging from basements and warehouses to parking spaces, and high adoption of the ghost kitchens because of the large range of benefits further influence the market. Additionally, increase in demand for digital ordering solutions, rapid urbanization, smart strategic marketing activities and use of the dark kitchen to test and identify foods before presenting them to consumers positively affect the cloud kitchen market. Furthermore, advancements in technology extend profitable opportunities to the market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, the high dependability on delivery applications and limited customer varieties as they are accessed through internet, are the major factors expected to obstruct the market growth. Concerns regarding consumption of high amount of carbs among population and high competition among players are projected to challenge the cloud kitchen market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

